M|Stic|tx|\| Feature adoption rates \| Weekly \| Core features used by 60%+ of actives \|
M|Stic|tx|\| cs health score \| Weekly \| 80%+ of cs in "healthy" range \|
M|Stic|tx|\| Net cs growth \| Monthly \| Positive and accelerating \|
